net.sf.jclal.activelearning.querystrategy

Class AbstractQueryStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclal.activelearning.querystrategy.AbstractQueryStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IConfigure, IQueryStrategy, JCLAL
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractMultiLabelQueryStrategy, AbstractSingleLabelQueryStrategy

    public abstract class AbstractQueryStrategy
extends java.lang.Object
implements IQueryStrategy, IConfigure
    Abstract class for active learning strategies. All AL query strategies must extend this class.
    Author:
    Oscar Gabriel Reyes Pupo, Eduardo Perez Perdomo
